  "detailed_description": "<strong>\"You are a shadow. Run to escape the Sunrise!\"</strong><br><br><i>Sunrise 7</i> is a 2D platforming adventure with a substantial difficulty level. Random upgrades and procedurally generated areas make each playthrough a new experience!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1261900/extras/62ed73e14bff6d2bf1c28020224125b8.poster.avif?t=1599246894\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1261900/extras/62ed73e14bff6d2bf1c28020224125b8.webm?t=1599246894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1261900/extras/62ed73e14bff6d2bf1c28020224125b8.mp4?t=1599246894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In <i>Sunrise 7</i>, a shadow awakens during the night, and must run to find shelter before the Sun rises! Powerful enemies and difficult challenges await in areas with unique themes and obstacles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1261900/extras/2da3acf9c565a71e4f7f702a4ca7e48f.poster.avif?t=1599246894\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1261900/extras/2da3acf9c565a71e4f7f702a4ca7e48f.webm?t=1599246894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1261900/extras/2da3acf9c565a71e4f7f702a4ca7e48f.mp4?t=1599246894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Absorb shade and choose specific abilities to level up and become strong enough to take on intense foes. Discover the world's secrets, and fight to defeat the Sunlight!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1261900/extras/d1034b838c95425ae40624afdd164e1a.poster.avif?t=1599246894\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1261900/extras/d1034b838c95425ae40624afdd164e1a.webm?t=1599246894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1261900/extras/d1034b838c95425ae40624afdd164e1a.mp4?t=1599246894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Procedurally Generated Areas and Puzzles<br></li><li> Exciting Boss Fights<br></li><li> Rewarding Optional Challenges</li></ul>",
